  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>We are looking for Office Administrator.</p><p>Whose responsibilities include:</p><p>· Answering phone calls</p><p>· Assist for Payroll process / generate Payslip base on\ntimesheet</p><p>· Arrange, schedule, coordinate Training whenever request\n(new & renew); Dormitory check-in/out and record managing</p><p>· Able to manage documents filing</p><p>· Assist for submitting claim to customer, Issuing PO to\nsupplier when require</p><p>· Laise with office suppliers</p><p>· Other duties in office administration matters and ad hoc\nas per request</p><p>· Proactive and able to work independent</p><p>Requirement:</p><p>Prefer candidate with related experience (construction\nfield).</p><p>Working days 6days.</p>",
